Rating: 4
My husband is a huge pepper hound and he's always lamenting the lack of available fruit-based salsas. I made this for him on a whim one afternoon and he couldn't scarf it down fast enough. I was a hero for like three days. It's a beautiful, easy, and sharply favored salsa. Highly recommend.

Rating: 4
This salsa is a little unconventional, but I love it. Its very adaptable to whatever you have on hand. I often use mango instead of papaya, and I love to add tomatillos when they are available. It goes well with many foods; my favorite is with a breakfast burrito.

