Rating: 4
I made this recipe but used diced fresh peaches and honeydew melon in place of the papayas and pineapples. I also used a few tablespoons of canned Ortega diced chilies in place of fresh jalapenos and it turned out GREAT! It was a hit at our family reunion, where several asked for the recipe. Definitely a keeper.

